This error beats me. I have copied the piece of code directly from the official PHPExcel documentation and I have searched for string "getRowIterator" in all PHPExcel class files - there is no such method.

Is this a syntax error in documentation? Is there getRowIterator() at all?

 

Thanx in advance!
getRowIterator() is in the PHPExcel_Worksheet class (/Classes/PHPExcel/Worksheet.php) because you iterate through the rows in a worksheet. Requires PHPExcel 1.6.7 or above
